skdetail:

Invocation Name: rainfall sounds
des: Let the calming sounds of rainfall soothe you right to sleep! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Rainfall Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
